{"tid":2018203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拾壹個月 你 仲記唔記得？","createTime":"2020-05-15T13:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T13:02:17.000Z","uid":83371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94a6c9b7c9171c3640299ccb2814da7a78228224","tid":2018203,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLKNtNZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLKNtNZ.jpg&h=a4f5eb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月15日<br />\n好似過咗好耐咁<br />\n但 只係11個月<br />\n你 仲記唔記得？<br />\n你 仲有無保持個一份憤怒<br />\n你 仲記唔記得佢？<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個月<br />\n分化 夠啦<br />\n內耗 夠啦<br />\n記唔記得佢交畀我地嘅任務<br />\n佢嘅遺願 我地做到未？<br />\n未嘅 就好醒啦<br />\n抖夠啦<br />\n<br />\n準備好未 <br />\n仲有 1個月"},{"pid":"3b7492b868b7618b0ef50a7bea18dc0da36e3294","tid":2018203,"uid":204872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}